WEBVTT

00:01.178 --> 00:05.935
Just 156 hits shy of 3000th for his Major League Baseball career,...

00:06.347 --> 00:11.484
...Ichiro Suzuki will continue to chase that milestone with the Miami Marlins at 2015.

00:11.966 --> 00:16.173
The ten-time all-star finalized his one-year deal with the club back on Tuesday...

00:16.497 --> 00:18.846
...and will enter his 15th Major League season.

